<p>Overall, Google Gravity offers a playful twist on a familiar interface by turning simple physics into a source of entertainment. Whether you’re experimenting freely, creating humorous setups, or taking on the added challenge of lava mode, the game rewards curiosity and experimentation. It’s a great example of how small interactive ideas can transform an everyday search page into a memorable and engaging experience.</p>
